Project.Description: The project is a multimillion-dollar project in Bloomington, IL to Minonk Il. It’s a large 20 mile 345 kv transmission line that is scheduled to start at the Oracle Innovations Lab Switchyard and it will have multiple spans crossing I-39. The project is in construction phase and has been running for 8 months. The owner has a number of sub-contractors they’re working with to get this done to turnover to operations by year end.
